title: How to Celebrate Through Jealousy
description:
Sadie speaks with DawnCheré Wilkerson about fighting jealousy with celebration and the importance of knowing your worth. They also get into things to look for when dating, leading yourself first, and the importance of community. God never wastes a waiting season and his ultimate calling on your life is much more simple than you might think.
